     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                    Test 21 History file
                    --------------------
This file should be used by the test developer to briefly
summarize all major modifications introduced in the code and keep
track of all tags.

     ----------------------------------------------------------
     * Reverse chronological order (last date on top), please *
     ----------------------------------------------------------

15 jun 2011, Gunter Folger              (test21-V09-04-01)
- update physics list to be closer to QGSC

29 Mar 2011, Gunter Folger              (test21-V09-04-00)
- Correct GNUmakefile_hadronic_exerciser to work with global shared libs.

4 Feb 2010,  Mikhail Kosov (test21-V09-03-00)
- Use separate MultipleScattering for e, Mu, and h=hadrons
- Updated README (run instruction)

20 October 2009,  Hisaya Kurashige (test21-V09-02-01)
- Use /run/setCut instead of /run/particle/setCut
 
26 May 2009, Gunter Folger		( test21-V09-02-00 )
- rename hadronic exerciser files; use "_" instead of "." in filename; 
   ("." in fileanme confuses Windows, resulting in warnings)

6th December 2005  Gabriele Cosmo
- Trivial changes for support of CLHEP-2.0.X series.

16th March 2004  Gabriele Cosmo
- Fixed compilation warnings.
- Replaced usage of NULL with 0.

1st November 2001  Hans-Peter Wellisch
- New test provided.
